Append

Append Procedure Generates all Default Values for all Fields in a Record. Set its State as New Record but not Modified Record. Does not Generate an IRecSerialization Append Generate a New GUID for the record while Clear sets the GUID to GUID_NULL (Overrides TJanuaRecord.Append.)
